name: NavThems Lazy Load
author: navthemes

sections.description:
This plugin helps to improve loading speed and page insight by implemeting lazy load.

Features:

  • Simple setup – Just install plugin and you done.

Support

If you have any questions please let us know directly at enquiry@navthemes.com.
sections.installation:
1. Install NavThems Lazy Load either via WordPress.org plugin repository or directly by uploading the files to your server
  2. Activate the plugin through the Plugins menu in your WordPress dashboard
sections.faq:
After installing is there anything else i need to do ?

Nope. you just have to install it and it will start its magic right away.
